      <title>托克表示，随着新技术推动电力消耗，铜需求将蓬勃发展</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/copper-demand-boom-new-technology-drives-power-consumption-trafigura-says-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大宗商品交易商托克告诉路透社，电动汽车、电力基础设施、人工智能和自动化领域的蓬勃发展将导致未来十年至少增加 1000 万吨铜消耗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/copper-demand-boom-new-technology-drives-power-consumption-trafigura-says-2024-04-22/</guid>
